---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Overview - PROSPERO">
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-section-padding overflow-hidden bg-surface bg-[url('/images/project-logos/getsitelogo.png')] bg-contain bg-center bg-no-repeat">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur-sm z-0"></div>
        <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-8 relative z-10 text-center">
            <h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg tracking-tight text-sovereign-blue mb-stack-md">Overview</h1>
            <p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                PROSPERO advances programmable and scalable operations for efficient, resource-aware architecture in 6G networks.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-section-padding bg-surface-container-lowest">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-8 space-y-stack-md font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            <p>
                The project focuses on sovereign, sustainable, and simplified 6G infrastructure. Its approach converges connectivity, computing, and intelligence to support resilient European technological sovereignty.
            </p>
            <p>
                PROSPERO builds on the evolution of mobile network architecture by targeting resource awareness, native AI integration, global operation, and simplified orchestration across the compute-connectivity continuum.
            </p>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 pt-stack-md">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-glass-stroke shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)]">
                    <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Vision</h2>
                    <p class="font-body-md text-body-md">A transparent, efficient, and programmable 6G ecosystem aligned with European digital sovereignty.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-glass-stroke shadow-[0_4px_20px_rgba(0,0,0,0.03)]">
                    <h2 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-primary mb-2">Scope</h2>
                    <p class="font-body-md text-body-md">Architecture, intelligence, validation, dissemination, and open research outputs for future networks.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
